User Table:
- user_id (Primary Key)
- username
- email
- password_hash
- registration_date

Island Table:
- island_id (Primary Key)
- latitude
- longitude
- island_area
- detection_time
- user_id (Foreign Key to User Table)

Comment Table:
- comment_id (Primary Key)
- island_id (Foreign Key to Island Table)
- user_id (Foreign Key to User Table)
- comment_text
- attachment_type (e.g., image, video)
- attachment_url
- comment_time
